  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oryks is a 2D platform game inspired by the Halloween atmosphere like in Tim Burton's films.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character, commissioned by the mysterious cult \"Oryks\", must investigate paranormal activity in a certain town </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and its surroundings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/09dd315a9a7719065bc89e1e2a1dd15f.poster.avif?t=1732657273\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/09dd315a9a7719065bc89e1e2a1dd15f.webm?t=1732657273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/09dd315a9a7719065bc89e1e2a1dd15f.mp4?t=1732657273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct investigations and fight various dark creatures, from ghosts to vampires, using various weapons and methods to defeat them, all in the atmosphere of an autumn Halloween evening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/6a6e082ecfeafae9d2d5399d6df5e4c5.poster.avif?t=1732657273\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/6a6e082ecfeafae9d2d5399d6df5e4c5.webm?t=1732657273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966580/extras/6a6e082ecfeafae9d2d5399d6df5e4c5.mp4?t=1732657273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D platform game inspired by the Halloween atmosphere like in Tim Burton's films.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, we conduct conversations, solve investigations, move left and right, jump and shoot to defeat enemies, we also interact with the environment. We also make decisions that affect the course of the mission.</p>",
